The lonely necromancer
The cause of the undead activity in Canian territory is an old necromancer. He has managed to create a very powerful spell that does not allow the undead to rest peacefully in their graves.
#subobj 1
Get to the Island of Death
You can only get to the island by taking the bridge to the west of the area.
#subobj 2
Get to the necromancer's house
The necromancer lives in his hut, surrounded by dead animals. He never leaves his hiding place.
#subobj 3
Set fire to the hut
To expel the Necromancer and take him prisoner you must start a fire.
#subobj 4
Escort the prisoner away
Only with the help of the necromancer can you remove the cause of undead activity.